snippet.title: Alan Walker - On My Way (Epic Metal Cover by SoniKhaos)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
Symmetric Chaos Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SymmetricChaos

Ever since I was a kid, whenever I heard a Tetris theme, I used to think that it would be really cool if that melody became a guitar solo. But I didn't know how to play the guitar well, and I didn't have the ability to turn my imagination into reality. When "On My Way" was first released two years ago, as soon as I heard it, I immediately thought that it was a perfect fit for Tetris. However, it wasn't that easy. I wanted to come up with a more dramatic development, but due to limitations in communication with the members, I almost gave up on this project. As time passed, I happened to tell Patrick about the project, and a few days later he presented a sketch of a song that was so epic and grandiose. And through countless revisions, he succeeded in drawing out all my imagination to the limit and sublimating it even more beautifully. And this is the result.

Alan Walker - On My Way (Epic Metal Cover by SoniKhaos)

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Vocals, Mixing, Mastering, and Video Editing 
Patrick Fallang (Symmetric Chaos, Norway) - Guitars, Music Arrangement, and Producing

#PUBG #EpicMetal
